President Cyril Ramaphosa delivering his first May Day speech as
president of the ANC. The main event is held at the Isaac Wolfson Stadium at KwaZakhele in
Port Elizabeth in the Eastern Cape. The day was chaotic last year as workers prevented former
president Jacob Zuma from addressing the event and a fight broke out between
Zuma's supporters and those who were against him. WATCH LIVE BROADCAST BELOW:  